anded in whatever way she deems fit (again write ups, cleaning bathrooms, back to back shifts of closing one evening at 11 then being back to work to open at 8 am etc etc). She has also has been known to take out her problems on the workers...especially the ones she knows will not fight back...if she is having trouble with her home life she will bring it to work and make us all miserable...if she is late to work and someone else is late to work she will pull them into the office and reprimand them for being late even though she was late (this has happened to me on one occasion and a fellow worker at least once that I know of) these are just things that come to mind right now...there are a whole slew of other things she has done or does...<br>
